title: Powers Act
extract: This means that the actual regulatory powers provisions are contained within the Regulatory Powers Act, and the 'triggering' Act merely references the Regulatory Powers Act and expressly identifies which provisions of the triggering Act the Regulatory Powers Act will enforce.Aug 1, 2018
